Mini Alpino Corpus Tool (act)
=============================
DaniÃ«l de Kok <me@danieldk.eu>

Introduction
------------

Alpino includes the 'act' utility written in Python to create and extract
compact corpora. This tool works great, but has some dependencies that we
do not or can not install for distributed. mini-act implements a tiny subset
of act, specifically:

- Creating act corpora
- Listing corpus contents
- Extract all or specific corpus files.

Compilation
___________

Requirements:

- A decent C++ compiler.
- Some luck.

